Actions.Text: HELD FOR CONSIDERATION IN REAL PROPERTY TAXATION

Title: Provides a tax exemption on real property owned by members of volunteer fire companies in a certain county
Summary: Provides a tax exemption on real property owned by members of volunteer fire companies in counties with a population of more than 330,000 but less than 345,000.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the real property tax law, in relation to providing a tax exemption on real property owned by members of volunteer fire companies in a certain county
